  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the <strong>brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to a boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 15-20 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and rinse in a sieve under <strong>cold running water </strong>until completely cooled (leave in the sieve to drain fully!)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2370-Step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2370-Step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2370-Step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2370-Step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2370-Step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>ginger </strong>and <strong>chilli </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) to a bowl with the <strong>red</strong> <strong>Thai curry paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2370-Step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2370-Step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
