          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2370-Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove and discard the skin from the <strong>salmon fillets</strong>, then chop the<strong> salmon</strong> into small bite-sized cubes and add to the bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and use your hands to gently massage the mixture for 30 secs or until it comes together (clean hands is best!)</p><p>Tip: Don't squeeze the mixture too much, or this will release liquid and you want to keep the mixture dry</p>",
